    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>这里记录我 <del>乱搞</del> 实验过的写博客的工具</p><p><strong><strong>说明：附有学习视频教程，全部来源于b站，侵权联系删除</strong></strong></p><a id="more"></a><h2 id="hexo"><a href="#hexo" class="headerlink" title="hexo"></a>hexo</h2><p>（静态，免费，+github<br><a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1Yb411a7ty" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1Yb411a7ty</a></p><p>贴上主题：<br><a href="https://github.com/litten/hexo-theme-yilia" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://github.com/litten/hexo-theme-yilia</a><br><a href="https://github.com/Sariay/hexo-theme-Annie" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://github.com/Sariay/hexo-theme-Annie</a><br><a href="https://github.com/miiiku/flex-block" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://github.com/miiiku/flex-block</a></p><p><a href="https://molunerfinn.com/hexo-theme-melody-doc/zh-Hans/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://molunerfinn.com/hexo-theme-melody-doc/zh-Hans/</a></p><p><a href="https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/README.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/README.md</a></p><p>主题相关配置自行百度</p><h2 id="hugo"><a href="#hugo" class="headerlink" title="hugo"></a>hugo</h2><p>（静态，免费，比上面简单点，+github<br><a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1q4411i7gL" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1q4411i7gL</a></p><h2 id="typecho"><a href="#typecho" class="headerlink" title="typecho"></a>typecho</h2><p>（动态， 腾讯云或阿里云<br><a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1o4411r7x5?p=8" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1o4411r7x5?p=8</a></p><p>主题：<a href="https://typecho.me/1284.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://typecho.me/1284.html</a></p><h2 id="Gridea"><a href="#Gridea" class="headerlink" title="Gridea"></a>Gridea</h2><p>（静态，免费，+GitHub， 有客户端<br><a href="https://fehey.com/post/hve-notes-start/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://fehey.com/post/hve-notes-start/</a><br><a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/av69627579/?spm_id_from=333.788.videocard.0" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.bilibili.com/video/av69627579/?spm_id_from=333.788.videocard.0</a></p><h2 id="wordpress"><a href="#wordpress" class="headerlink" title="wordpress"></a>wordpress</h2><p>( 动态<br><a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1k4411e7Jn" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1k4411e7Jn</a></p><p>贴个主题：<a href="https://2heng.xin/theme-sakura/#toc-head-17" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://2heng.xin/theme-sakura/#toc-head-17</a></p><h2 id="推荐："><a href="#推荐：" class="headerlink" title="推荐："></a>推荐：</h2><p>静态博客推荐使用hexo（小白的话，Gridea也还行，可能速度不快），动态博客就…<del>博客园吧</del>…wordpress和typecho都行，其实博客园挺好用的。</p><h2 id="其他"><a href="#其他" class="headerlink" title="其他"></a>其他</h2><p>没玩过</p><p>建议喜欢折腾的人就玩到这吧…博客多不如博文多，博客好看不如博文精致…有任何疑问可以考虑看看视频里的弹幕，或者联系我</p><p>感谢上面的up主们。 侵权联系删除</p><p>搁笔。</p>]]></content>
    
